Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢的說 御門老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須把身體好好洗乾淨才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是花季少女要具備的休養喔 小靜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體已經長得這麼成熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話隨時都可以準備墜入愛河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是身為幽靈的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能這樣悠閒的生活著 這全都是托御門老師的福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也同樣要感謝妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了小靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能取得寶貴的思念體樣本資料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念體？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從超越特定種類的智慧生命體中誕生的精神能量體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 像小靜妳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的宇宙尖端科技把稱作幽靈的物體都給研究解釋清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是能量體 如果硬要施加精神的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有會消失的可能喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要適度而行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 我也沒有什麼煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒有必要擔心小靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要進行戰鬥訓練嗎 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然睡個大頭覺 好好休息下也不錯的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想修正下因為過度和平的生活而變的懶散的這張臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 自從在廢品商那裡撿到你以來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過我在這張床上睡過覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…倒是沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不要再叫我主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始叫我小闇就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知上一次熟睡離現在已經有多長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對自己的事情感覺記得不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從來沒有回頭去想過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後 什麼事情都記得非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九條學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前好像美柑承蒙您的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 真是非常的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意 我只是做了自己該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓沙姬大人看到我和你聊得這麼親密的話 事情就變複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和人家謝個禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 感覺怎麼樣 九條同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳拿的那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個東西該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇 不可以碰那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城 小闇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要誤會 西連寺 古手川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中是有原因的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大姐做的小發明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆手粘在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 好像是塞利奴擅自拿出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣 不管怎麼弄都不會開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手就像強力的吸鐵石一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對的說 過一段時間 吸力就變弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前就這樣一直和你牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買鯛魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是放學之後的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知羞恥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去 芽亞也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來很有趣 但是今天我有事情要辦的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是感覺好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起牽著手走著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感覺非常地不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和男朋友一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我和平時一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 都牽著手呢 如此親密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好和男朋友相處喔 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯛魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢偷吃的話 小心我切了你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑的色瞇瞇的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘得好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了竟然有這麼好用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗 大家都在看著呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我也沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是用了那個了的話 我就也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽亞沒有跟過來還真是意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為以她的性格 一定會插一腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小闇和梨斗那種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不要草率行動的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟美柑說了 她說一定要我們到家去吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇小時候是怎樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要得寸進尺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是和身為「目標」的你能說的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美柑做的料理吃不下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也幫我吃一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇 前一陣子教妳的切丁方法妳完全掌握了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切絲也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切片也可以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有進行特訓…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫上美柑的忙 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人配合的真完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來小闇也不是蓋的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢 小闇 給妳添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到效果消失為止 請慢慢享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的為什麼我要做這種事情啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的話 就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小闇?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想洗個澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡什麼的…可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和梨斗一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一天不洗也沒有問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一天一定要洗一次澡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上也有點汗臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請好好洗洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候…我會用毛巾…擋住的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼美妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請無論如何也讓我一起進去幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 夢夢不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟著一起進去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜妳去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 我進去看著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢夢不管什麼都太偏袒梨斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧 小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意見呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是衣服怎麼脫啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪了不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我會用變身縫好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要把眼罩拿下來喔 梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遮住了眼睛也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫妳擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢 娜娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會給你洗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個花灑 花灑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個感覺是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是我的…尾巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭H的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 你這禽獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 娜娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和室裡鋪了被褥嗎？美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇說和梨斗兩個人睡在床上有點擠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈說到早上效果差不多就會消了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一樓的話 就算發生了什麼也沒法立即阻止喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是小闇喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是夢夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起宇宙第一的殺手 更加戒備我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪糕 雪糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是… 芽亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是位普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是個可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說不定是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為幽靈的我去附身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探查她的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽亞究竟是怎樣的人就一目了然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟要和小闇一起睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和菈菈一起睡的時候也很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過和小闇睡覺卻有另一種緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…手上還留著剛剛的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在想什麼齷蹉的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做出什麼奇怪的動作就立馬幹掉你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇也睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從做了殺手之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直無法安然入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是讓身體得到休息 而盡量不讓自己睡得太熟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣的話 就無法知道敵人從哪裡進攻過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不繃緊神經的話 只要一瞬就會沒命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直活在一個很厲害的世界裡呢 小闇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 第一次遇到的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在為什麼而道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也包括啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對於小闇至今說了很多了不起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 全部都是出自我認真考慮的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想在小闇看來會認為是什麼都不懂囂張個什麼勁的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亞悠·露娜緹依克博士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…和你牽手之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起了她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你說一點往事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…芽亞的內心世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 請繼續舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔舔真是好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場面是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人到底在想些什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續去更深一點的地方看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠探聽到芽亞身分的什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想知道關於金色之闇所在之地的情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得那麼可愛還打算賺取賞金嗎 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確我們知道那傢伙在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們可沒那麼好免費將獵物的情報告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳能稍微陪我們玩一會兒我們倒是可以考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…就好像小闇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…一群沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過總算是肯老實交代了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於小闇姐姐的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺取賞金的遊戲也該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去吧 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇和夢夢都想知道的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能知道這點 我就立大功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是停手比較好喔 村雨學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做御門醫生的助手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是思念體嗎 還是第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我一樣做到精神入侵這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續讓妳留在我的體內可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再稍微遲一點離開我體內的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就會被消滅掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.43,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四角警告のイエローカード  ギリギリセーフ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.43,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點被罰 四角警告的黃牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:13.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角関係のトラブル アウト
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:13.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是三角關係引起的麻煩 Out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:18.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を見ると 反則したくなちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:18.33,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你我就有一種想犯規的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:21.78,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さあ ピンチもチャンスも纏めて All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:21.78,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 不管是危機還是機會 All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:24.67,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用意周到もルールも読まずにゴー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:24.67,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視用意周到的規則 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:30.67,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君に逢うたび 全部の気持ち ずっとグルグルしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:30.67,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次見到你 我就管不住我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:39.21,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭の中 君は誰とランデブーしてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:39.21,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子裡幻想著和你約會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:48.91,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとワクワクするレベル 試してみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:48.91,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想試試更進一步的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:51.20,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これは恋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:51.20,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:55.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空より広い 海よりも深い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:55.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比天還廣 比海還深
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:01.43,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河の果ての星の波にも収まりきらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:01.43,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是銀河盡頭的群星 也無法匹敵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:02.98,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと恋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:02.98,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:07.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定しても 言うこと聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:07.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我怎麼否定 我的心依然不聽使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.34,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸の鼓動が高鳴ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.34,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著清晰地心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:14.53,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもドキドキ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:14.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是撲通撲通的
